information.author: Centreon

description.value:
**Plugin Pack to monitor Azure Application Insights service using RestAPI or AZCLI.**

Available Host template and related Services:

|Cloud-Azure-Network-ApplicationInsights-custom|
|---|
|Cpu|   
|Memory| 
|Requests|            
|Exceptions|     
|Availability|   
|IO-Operations|  
|External-Calls|   
|Browser-Timings|

This Plugin Pack provides a Host discovery *provider* to be used with the Host discovery module.

**Plugin Pack pour superviser les resources Azure Application Insights via RestAPI ou AZCLI.**

Modèle d\'hôte disponibles et services associés:

|Cloud-Azure-Network-ApplicationInsights-custom|
|---|
|Cpu|    
|Memory| 
|Requests|            
|Exceptions|     
|Availability|   
|IO-Operations|  
|External-Calls|   
|Browser-Timings|

Ce Plugin Pack fournit un *provider* Host Discovery pour le module d\'auto-découverte d\'Hôtes
